Package jdk.test.lib.hotspot.ir_framework

Class IRNode

java.lang.Object
jdk.test.lib.hotspot.ir_framework.IRNode
public class IRNode extends Object
This class provides default regex strings that can be used in @IR annotations to specify IR constraints.

There are two types of default regexes:

  • Standalone regexes: Use them directly.

  • Composite regexes: Their names contain "_OF" and expect another string in a list in IR.failOn() and IR.counts(). They cannot be use as standalone regex and will result in a TestFormatException when doing so.

See Also:
IR
